name: Miss DIVA Shoe Greeting Card
description:
My classic design has made a return for all the DIVAs out there. 

Orange and red sorbet stripes the DIVA has a new look. Stamped with a dye based high heel, decorated with a red rhinestone and red polyester ribbon this DIVA is ready for show.

This is a great card for your friend, daughter and any family member who knows what it means to be a DIVA...

Card measures 5x7, comes with envelope and is blank inside but can be personalized with your special words and/or message.

name: Dr Seuss Custom Birthday Card
description:
I designed a card similar for a client off-line and loved the thought of it so much I made this one for Etsy.

Cover:
EVERYTHING SEUSS

The card is 5x7 inches red card stock. 2 shades of blue layered with white card stock. The white card stock is computer graphic and hand art mixed. In the corner I added Horton and Mr Brown. They are raised 1/4" off the card surface to give the card life. 

The inside will be printed with your message or Party info.
I will contact you ASAP after your order is received to figure the inside info/wording.

This order comes with 25 invitations, 25 white envelopes @ $1.65 per card which is not set in stone b/c I would like to discuss the card process and be sure of the characters you want on the card.

name: Treasured Friends Abstract Print Design Greeting Card
description:
This card... I felt like it was better to do something not so out there or loud but a card that was... Art!

This card is 5x7 with a combination match print of a floral design. The inside is blank and it comes with a white envelope. The embellished insert is cardboard like with a flower attachement.

This is sure to be a great card for that beloved friend. A card you can use for any and all occasions to come.

**Card(s) ships USPS First Class Mail and is delivered in protective plastic. Card(s) ships out 2-4 days after order and may take 3-5 days (depending on your location) to arrive. I can also ship the card directly to your recipient.
